1. Brainstorm two claims on the CON side;
2. Convey your ideas based on the two claims with your teammate through Chat (the button locates at the right side of the system);
3. Provide feedbacks and make reflections on your teammates' claims;
Write down the claims you have thought of;
4. Discuss over backings (facts/evidence/reasoning/examples/data/references) to support the propositions you just composed and write them down in the backing area.
5. Collaboratively compose another one or more arguments either in correspondence with the PRO ones, or add a new pair to develop more interesting arguments.

